@rem 
@rem FUNCTION
@rem 
@rem    Returns information about a given Zone Time Band.
@rem 
@rem SEE ALSO
@rem 
@rem    @{"Getting Results" link "ONLINEMETER_AREXX_GETTING_RESULTS"}
@rem 
